{"tid":1368471,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[曾因(社會氣氛)而不加場] 謝安琪開心宣布演唱會加場","createTime":"2019-07-26T13:22:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T01:46:46.000Z","uid":197644,"like":33,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"13211a53bfd719ec5a900da2b9426bbef016b3bf","tid":1368471,"uid":197644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:22:18.000Z","msg":"2016年：「<span style=\"color: red;\">呢個社會氣氛下，我地冇辦法大鑼大鼓情緒高漲地宣傳演唱會、宣布加場！</span>」<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">完整訪問：藉著《 FACE》說再見 謝安琪小休前終極專訪：「唔介意係唔係天后！」 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.face.nextmedia.com/article/462/17723479\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.face.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F462%2F17723479&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07u2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=227bbf05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.face.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F462%2F17723479&h=b9e622b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.face.nextmedia.com/article/462/17723479</a> <br />\n<a href=\"http://hittt.blogspot.com/2016/03/face-face-462-mf.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhittt.blogspot.com%2F2016%2F03%2Fface-face-462-mf.html&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07u2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=181bacd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hittt.blogspot.com/2016/03/face-face-462-mf.html</a></span><br />\n<br />\n2019年個社會氣氛就好好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好到今天宣布加場<br />\n對於加開一場，<span style=\"color: red;\">Kay受訪時表示很開心</span>，因為檔期很短，只許加開一場，不能再加。<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190726/1564136510310\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190726%2F1564136510310&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07u2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=d4da64ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190726%2F1564136510310&h=bf3d21f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190726/1564136510310</a></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190726/s00009/c9db76c1c385d00d7e5e8e77c6980cc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20190726%2Fs00009%2Fc9db76c1c385d00d7e5e8e77c6980cc6.jpg&h=54dff2d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n呢個女人真係好假<br />\n2016年滯銷就賴社會氣氛，而唔加場<br />\n2019年就開心加場<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20160412/s00007/673a6142a5afb6fc13ff830aeaf91af9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20160412%2Fs00007%2F673a6142a5afb6fc13ff830aeaf91af9.jpg&h=40010de7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b10fac503a38da3174250f5a85922a01875c7c91","tid":1368471,"uid":197644,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:13:11.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8c6933b14a0e1b0dc4db65103cafc14d8be915","tid":1368471,"uid":53705,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:09:24.000Z","msg":"你行過 金拱門, 會見到佢既廣告<br />\n<br />\n口說民主, 身體很誠實奶大陸"},{"pid":"4e9b9cc061a4396c04ebb220840fc5d3a10ac656","tid":1368471,"uid":217411,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:22:43.000Z","msg":"佢下爬個假體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac652e404fd51070aef2a3f95b5f34e71dae40a7","tid":1368471,"uid":52605,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:05:09.000Z","msg":"冇㗎啦 以前就唱抗爭歌曲<br />\n而家就唱埋啲淫歌<br />\n偷情做主題嘅歌都唱？"},{"pid":"abec089f56f407980c0404cf78996f436e2399eb","tid":1368471,"uid":33933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢就無人反"},{"pid":"7af9801defc0b2